\item[$(8)$] obabxnu $15$ koLaga, obabxnu $20$ koLaga, obabxnu $4$
    KaMDdi, dhAyxnayxgaLanunx tegedukoMDu saMtege hoVgi, oMdeV
    dhAraNeyalilx mAri oMdeV samanAda dhanavanunx paDakoMDa karxma
    hAyxge?

