    $4$ KaMDagadavanu & $1$ & $3$ & $26$ & = & $78$ & $2$ koLaga
    \end{tabular}}

    eraDaneV dhAraNe $1$ koLagakekx $7$ haNada meVrige,

    \begin{tabular}{rl}
